name: Hamilton U.S. Financials YIELD MAXIMIZER TM ETF
longDescription: The Fund will seek to achieve its investment objective by investing in an equal-weight largecap equity portfolio of financial services companies domiciled/listed primarily in the United States. FMAX may also hold cash and cash equivalents or other money market instruments in order to meet its obligations. The investment objective of FMAX is to deliver attractive monthly income, while providing exposure to an equalweighted equity portfolio of financial services companies.
